Package org.apache.commons.collections4.iterators

Class UnmodifiableMapIterator<K,​V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.collections4.iterators.UnmodifiableMapIterator<K,​V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of keys
    V - the type of mapped values
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<K>, MapIterator<K,​V>, Unmodifiable
    public final class UnmodifiableMapIterator<K,​V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements MapIterator<K,​V>, Unmodifiable
    Decorates a map iterator such that it cannot be modified.

    Attempts to modify it will result in an UnsupportedOperationException.

    Since:
    3.0
